Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.68,1:15:40.84,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Reflecting in the mirror that day was a dazzling silhouette
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.84,1:15:46.99,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,I stood there, longing for that lovely figure
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.99,1:15:53.14,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,It became a habit to chide and scold
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.14,1:15:59.14,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,the part of you that stuck out from that “innocent” comment
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.14,1:16:05.46,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Even if we don’t say anything, somehow it still gets through
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.46,1:16:10.88,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,These emotions and this nervousness are all your doing, aren’t they?!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.34,1:16:15.05,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,As we laugh together lots and motivate one another,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.05,1:16:18.28,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,the feelings that pile up in layers are a mille-feuille
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.28,1:16:23.60,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,A rainbow-colored harmony is playing
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.60,1:16:27.45,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Before, I shed tears out of frustration at saying bye-bye
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.45,1:16:35.46,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Now this clumsy me can say it without crying:
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.46,1:16:37.18,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Bye, see you again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.49,1:16:54.72,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Lately, you’ve just been gazing up at the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.72,1:17:00.74,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,You tell me of your endless dreams with unwavering eyes, but
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.74,1:17:06.92,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,when you undo your ribbon, it’s a sign that you’re turning into an adult
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.92,1:17:12.94,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Don’t go away and leave me behind, complaints like that feel like slipping out
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.94,1:17:19.26,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,When your knee are side by side with mine, I get fired up
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.26,1:17:24.64,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,With the warmth you transmit me, my bluffing heart melts away gently
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.20,1:17:28.98,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,As we play with each other lots and even as we get mad
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.98,1:17:32.13,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,this mille-feuille of feelings won’t collapse
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.13,1:17:37.44,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,This pride of mine won’t be broken, not by anyone
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.44,1:17:41.25,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Absolutely! want to convey it in my own fashion
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.25,1:17:49.26,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Even if I’m incomplete, I’ll say it without any embarrassment:
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.26,1:17:51.10,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you, always
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.05,1:18:22.34,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,The color of the very first cellphone strap
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.34,1:18:27.81,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,that you gave me to match yours has faded since then, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.34,1:18:32.09,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,As we laugh together and motivate one another all through our lives,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.09,1:18:35.17,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,I want our friendship to pile up layers, like a mille-feuille
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.17,1:18:40.60,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,All over the world, a rainbow-colored harmony
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.60,1:18:44.36,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Before, I shed tears out of frustration at bye-bye
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.36,1:18:52.32,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Now this clumsy me can say it without crying:
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.32,1:18:54.00,Toptitle,,0,0,0,,Bye, see you again tomorrow
